data.text:
Premier Mortgage Resources, LLC (“PMR”) uses multiple systems to efficiently communicate important information to our customers. By clicking submit, you are also providing express written consent for PMR to contact you, using the information you provided above and/or the information you provide in your initial application to PMR, which may also be noted above, including phone (land, mobile, or VoIP), email address, and/or mailing address, to include contacting you through automated means, such as 1) autodialing, text, and pre-recorded messaging via telephone, 2) mobile device, including SMS and MMS, and/or 3) email, even if you are on a corporate, state, or national Do Not Call Registry. Note that your consent is not a requirement of obtaining a loan, or otherwise, a condition of purchasing any property, goods, or services and you can opt out of receiving these communications at any point in time.

Premier Mortgage Resources LLC” may send text messages to my wireless phone number for any purpose. Message and data rates may apply. Message frequency will vary, and you will be able to Opt-out by replying “STOP”. For more information on how your data will be handled please see visit https://www.pmrloans.com/privacy-policy/.
